{
  "text": "I just meant was it possible to say for a green ray when we're talking about uh green ray activation and energy transfers. Is it possible for a green ray uh person who is uh primarily green ray activation to vary on both sides of green ray uh a large or small amount in uh energy activation, or does he stay primarily green ray? I am Ra. We grasp the newness of material requested by you. It was unclear for we thought we had covered this material. The portion we have covered is this. The green array activation is always vulnerable to the yellow or orange ray of opposition, this being a largely yellow ray, but often coming into orange ray, fear of possession, a desire for possession, fear of being possessed, a desire to be possessed. These are the distortions which will cause the deactivation of green ray energy a transfer. The new material is this. Once the green ray has been achieved, the ability of the entity to enter a blue ray is immediate and is only awaiting the efforts of the individual. The indigo array is opened only through considerable discipline and a practice, largely having to do with acceptance of a self, not only as the polarized and a balanced self, but as the creator, as an entity of infinite worth. This will begin to activate the indigo ray.",
